project-archived-desc-more: All open source projects are subject to a lifecycle and can become less active for a number of reasons. Inside NCC, projects are expected to maintain a number of requirements, and if these are not met, a proposal can be submitted to the NCC PMC to archive a project.
project-other-desc: They used to be part of the NCC, but currently they belong to other respective communities and are no longer members of this community. They are also no longer authorized to use the community's images or textual logos for promotion.
